name: Pirate Fairies of the 8th Sea
description:
Pirate Fairies of the 8th Sea - written and illustrated by George Webber of NoCashComics.com

The opening story of Captain Minou and her pirate crew bound for treasure and adventure, that is if nothing gets in her way.

Digital Comic, Black & White, 24 pages

name: ALLEY CATS - Birds of a Feather
description:
"ALLEY CATS" is a short story written and illustrated by George Webber of NoCashComics.

While Alley Cats is a short story it's an oddly up lifting tale of a resigned yet kind hearted Streetwalker and a Con Artist Alley Cat among the urban grim whom together find something they weren't really aware they needed but clearly have always wanted.

In the end like Aesop's fables the moral of the story that says it all.

Digital Comic Book in PDF format, 8 pages plus covers Black & White.

READER COMMENTS:

I know my hookers, and this one is worth every buck!
Enjoyed it, real sweet and cute.

- Jimmy Palmiotti (Writer & Inker - Jonah Hex - Deadpool - Painkiller Jane)

Why are you not famous? Eisner worthy art and a great ass too.

- Jason McNamara (Wrter - The Martian Confederacy - First Moon)
